reviewText: The Power Rangers are back in Power Rangers Zeo. this is the new power rangers show that left off the original show and alien rangers. with the rangers new powers the zeo crystals they now face an even worse enemy the machine empire which is ruled by king mondo and his wife machinea and their son prince sprocket. the rangers need this new power to defeat them. this is a great show. but I still do favor the original. this is a great season and here are the best episodes of season 1Episodes1. reviewText: This power rangers season or Zeo is awesome. The machine empire is the new foe so there are lots of robots and mechas instead of the usual beasts and monsters.  Funny and ridiculous script writing.Hope to see vol. 2 soon!Overall the Zeo season is fantastic. Recommended.

reviewText: I recently bought all of the Mighty Morphin section of Power Rangers Series, and as a kid I stopped watching when I got more into girls, and having friends and homework, ect... But watching it again, I remember all my toys I once owned and the 'good' things I do have seemed to be things I have learned from watching this show as a kid. I thought I would stop watching at the end of the Mighty Morphin Power Rangers, But I got sucked in, FEED ME MAOR POWER RANGERS (in Goldars Voice)... So here I am watching Zeo continuing on where I left off as a kid.

reviewText: Well this is a budget way to save your money. But for die hards like me. We already own it in a 5 Dvd Set along with The Complete Series of Turbo, In Space and Lost Galaxy due to all Those being in the Complete Series not Volumes. So if u have the money..i reccommend on buying The 21 Dvd Box Set Power Rangers Seasons 4-7. Or u can Get This Volume and miss The Bonus Features Completely. BUT this would Probably Not Be A Good Seller. IT COMES OUT THE SAME DAY aS THE SEASONS 8-12 Box Set. Which i m getting.
summary: Cool. BUT HAVE the complete series due to the seasons 4-7 Box Set.

reviewText: at the end of mmpr season three the command center was left destroyed and the fate of zordon as well alpha five and the future of the rangers was left uncertain. after finding the zeo crystal which was dropped by rito and goldar the rangers enter a secret passage way and the command center somehow is rebuilt by the power of the zeo crystal. harnessing the zeo powers with the help of zordon and alpha who have survived as well billy who steps down as a ranger tommy, kat, adam, rocky and new ranger tanya become the next level of power rangers. if you enjoyed this series in the 90s relive the memories of this show by getting this dvd.
